%C - Use callback mode to dump raw frames.

Syntax:
    camera-dump-frame-no-screen [options]

Options
    -f Absolute path to a folder to where camera-dump-frame-no-screen dumps frames. Default folder path is /data/share/sensor.
    -u camera_unit Camera unit to use; if not specified, CAMERA_UNIT_1 will be used.

Examples
    camera-dump-frame-no-screen
    camera-dump-frame-no-screen -u 2
    camera-dump-frame-no-screen -f /data/home/qnxuser
